ns0:foreignObject.html:div: Look carefully at the image showing elements of the weather. Identify and understand the different parts shown in the illustration. Use your knowledge of science to answer the questions that follow.

ns0:svg.ns0:text: 1. What are the main elements visible in the weather illustration?
2. Can you identify and list the different types of clouds shown in the image?
3. What does the image suggest about the weather conditions? Is it sunny, rainy, or something else?
4. How do the elements shown in the image affect our daily activities or plans?
5. If you were to add one more element to the weather illustration to make it more realistic, what would it be and why?
